SEC Accuses Former Goldman ETF Trader of Insider Trading: Audio

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-21T21:44:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/sec-accuses-former-goldman-etf-trader-of-insider-trading-audio.html
 A former Goldman Sachs Group Inc.
trader and his father were accused by U.S. regulators of making 
illegal trades based on confidential information related to the 
firm's exchange-traded fund investments.  Bloomberg Radio's 
Catherine Cowdery reports on Exchange Traded Funds.   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 01:25
 